sweden rais fuel tax to fund defenc spend sweden announc tax increas on petrol and heat oil from juli 1 , 1987 to help financ a 1.7 pct rise in defenc spend over the next five year . a financ ministri statement said the increas should boost the price of petrol by 0.13 crown to an averag of 4.21 crown per litr while light-grad heat oil would go up by 30 crown per cubic metr to an averag of 1,665 crown . it said oil compani should absorb part of the tax rise intern and not pass it on to consum as compens for a reduct in the stock that the industri is requir to keep for sweden 's nation petroleum reserv .